{ loses to a long forcing sequence. } 22. Rxd6+ Qxd6 23. Qf5+ Qe6 24. Qb5+ Kd8
25. Qb8+ Qc8 26. Rd1+ Rd7 27. Bc7+
{ Exploiting two pins and winning the queen. } 27... Ke7 28. Re1+ Kf7 29. Qxc8
